@Node "history" "History"

V0.82
=====

- Spanish catalog
- New layout of the device settings. The main window is smaller now.
- New option "Open Midi Loop"
- Added support for stereo samples
- Added ARexx port
- ARexx-script for batch-dumping samples
- MIDI dump request implemented


V0.81
=====

- Learned WAVE and IFF-8SVX fileformats.
- You can now drop Samples into the main window.
- The sample frequency and the loop-points can be altered.
- Fixed a bug when dumping a 16-bit WAVE to SCSI.


V0.8
====

- Initial release.


